nagement services and make its technology platform available to finance professionals key figuresedit total client assets chf  billion assets under management chf  billion fitch rating aa ratio cet at  according to basel iii  activitiesedit the group is organised around three areas of activity with total client assets of chf  billion private clients lombard odier offers its private clients a range of wealth management solutions such as portfolio management under a discretionary or advisory mandate succession planning tax reporting or custody services asset management unit through its branch loim lombard odier investment managers lombard odier offers its clients riskbased asset allocation themed equity investments convertible bonds and absolute return strategies technology and banking services lombard odier provides clients of banking and technology services with access to its it and operational infrastructure as well as global custody and reporting services otheredit as a familyrun business the bank is actively committed to the promotion study and development of the family business model in addition through the fondation lombard odier the firm supports numerous philanthropic activities in the fields of innovation entrepreneurship and the training of young people key datesedit   foundation of hy hentsch  cie by henri hentsch   creation of the bank henri hentsch  lombard by henri hentsch and jean gédéon lombard   financiers of the mining industry   cofoundation of the geneva stock exchange  years before the zurich stock exchange   foundation by james odier and jules darierrey of the first life insurance company in geneva   involvement in the funding of the swiss rail network   cofoundation of the swiss national bank   implementation of a pension fund for the firms employees   pioneers in the creation and distribution of investment funds in europe   first private bank to set up an office abroad office opened in montreal   installation of the firms first it system   first european bank with a seat on the new york stock exchange   involvement in the implementation of the swiss electronic stock exchange   launch of first sectoral fund in collaboration with scientific experts   establishment of lombard odier darier hentsch  cie   creation of the lombard odier brand   new company name lombard odier  co   the bank becomes lombard odier  co ltd a corporate partnership société en commandite par actions see alsoedit banking in switzerland referencesedit  lombard odier  the partners lombardodiercom   a b cross systems bank lombard odier  co ltd  spba abpsch   lombard odier et mirabaud publient leurs premiers résultats hebdoch   the lombard odier group reports  results lombardodiercom   ludovic goix le groupe lombard odier publie ses résultats pour le er semestre  lelezardcom   die lombard odier gruppe veröffentlicht die ergebnisse für das  halbjahr  presseportalde   lombard odier  key dates lombardodiercom  companies portal geneva portal retrieved from httpsenwikipediaorgwindexphptitlebanklombardodiercooldid categories private banksbanks of switzerlandcompanies established in henokiens companies navigation menu personal tools not logged intalkcontributionscreate accountlog in namespaces article talk variants views read edit view history more search navigation main pagecontentsfeatured contentcurrent eventsrandom articledonate to wikipediawikipedia store interaction helpabout wikipediacommunity portalrecent changescontact page tools what links hererelated changesupload filespecial pagespermanent linkpage informationwikidata itemcite this page printexport create a bookdownload as pdfprintable version languages catalàdeutschespañolfrançaisitalianolietuvių edit links this page was last edited on  january  at  text is available under the creative commons attributionsharealike license additional terms may apply by using this site you agree to the terms of use and privacy policy wikipedia® is a registered trademark of the wikimedia foundation inc