es has a network of  offices covering  jurisdictions and employs around  people some years ago lombard odier decided to accelerate the development of its privateclient activities in europe asia and switzerland strengthen its asset management services and make its technology platform available to finance professionals key figuresedit total client assets chf  billion assets under management chf  billion fitch rating aa ratio cet at  according to basel iii  activitiesedit the group is organised around three areas of activity with total client assets of chf  billion private clients lombard odier offers its private clients a range of wealth management solutions such as portfolio management under a discretionary or advisory mandate succession planning tax reporting or custody services asset management unit through its branch loim lombard odier investment managers lombard odier offers its clients riskbased asset allocation themed equity investments convertible bonds and absolute return strategies technology and banking services lombard odier provides clients of banking and technology services with access to its it and operational infrastructure as well as global custody and reporting services otheredit as a familyrun business the bank is actively committed to the promotion study and development of the family business model in addition through the fondation lombard odier the firm supports numerous philanthropic activities in the fields of innovation entrepreneurship and the training of young people key datesedit   foundation of hy hentsch  cie by henri hentsch   creation of the bank henri hentsch  lombard by henri hentsch and jean gédéon lombard   financiers of the mining industry   cofoundation of the geneva stock exchange  years before the zurich stock exchange   foundation by james odier and jules darierrey of the first life insurance company in geneva   involvement in the funding of the swiss rail network   cofoundation of the swiss national bank   implementation of a p