 odier investment managers lombard odier offers its clients riskbased asset allocation themed equity investments convertible bonds and absolute return strategies technology and banking services lombard odier provides clients of banking and technology services with access to its it and operational infrastructure as well as global custody and reporting services otheredit as a familyrun business the bank is actively committed to the promotion study and development of the family business model in addition through the fondation lombard odier the firm supports numerous philanthropic activities in the fields of innovation entrepreneurship and the training of young people key datesedit   foundation of hy hentsch  cie by henri hentsch   creation of the bank henri hentsch  lombard by henri hentsch and jean gédéon lombard   financiers of the mining industry   cofoundation of the geneva stock exchange  years before the zurich stock exchange   foundation by james odier and jules darierrey of the first life insurance company in geneva   involvement in the funding of the swiss rail network   cofoundation of the swiss national bank   implementation of a pension fund for the firms employees   pioneers in the creation and distribution of investment funds in europe   first private bank to set up an office abroad office opened in montreal   installation of the firms first it system   first european bank with a seat on the new york stock exchange   involvement in the implementation of the swiss electronic stock exchange   launch of first sectoral fund in collaboration with scientific experts   establishment of lombard odier darier hentsch  cie   creation of the lombard odier brand   new company name lombard odier  co   the bank becomes lombard odier  co ltd a corporate partnership société en commandite par actions see alsoedit banking in switzerland referencesedit  lombard odier  the partners lombardodiercom   a b cross systems bank lombard odier  co ltd  spba abpsch   lombard odier et 